# SyncScript.app — curated knowledge index (not a copy of MEMORY.md)

**Source of truth for depth:** repo root **`MEMORY.md`** (curated handoff). **`SESSION_START.md`** for session focus. Raw logs: **`memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`**. This rule is a **routing table** so agents know *what to read* without pasting 400+ lines into every prompt.

## Production identity (fact-checked in MEMORY.md)

| Item | Value |
|------|--------|
| **Live site** | **`https://www.syncscript.app`** (Vercel; custom domain aliases latest prod deploy) |
| **GitHub** | **`stringerc/syncscriptE`**, branch **`main`** (confirm Vercel Git integration matches this repo) |
