| **API** | **`api/*.ts`** — Vercel serverless; **`npm run guard:vercel-functions`** (Hobby function cap) |
| **Supabase** | Project ref **`kwhnrlzibgfedtxpkbgb`**; Edge **`make-server-57781ad9`** — deploy: `npm run deploy:edge:make-server` with **`--use-api`** |
